            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Denekamp</placeName>
                <date>der 28 July</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">My very dear uncle:</p>
            <p>Although it is well a long time since I have<lb/> written you, and it is not so well
                from me,<lb/> that say myself; but on the other side<lb/>
                <sic>thougt</sic> always I receive every month a book<lb/> from you; and then I know
                also that you are<lb/> in good health; the same I can tell you from<lb/> my side and
                hope that our <hi rend="underline">Father</hi> may give you<lb/> health yet many
                years <add>Hebrew</add>......<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Also I have read in the last book that<lb/> aunt is dead in the
                month of <date>May</date>, it is well<lb/> good that God has taken her from this
                earth;<lb/> in her live was nothing here; then a man<lb/> how cannot see is very
                unhappy. My mother<lb/> says now I shall well receive a letter in<lb/> short time
                from your uncle, because the<lb/> aunt is dead. My dear uncle, if you write<lb/> my,
                to write a <sic>lettle</sic> greater than in the<lb/> last letter from you, are any
                words who I<lb/> cannot read, but therefore you must not be<lb/> angry on me.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Last week we have read every day in the<lb/> newspaper that
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> and the other<lb/> towns in
                    <placeName>Pennsylvania</placeName> should be declared in<lb/> state of seige,
                which make us very sorrowful<lb/>
                <sic>becauseyou</sic>; and my mother and father says<lb/> that you go to an other
                land where the war<lb/> does not rule, than where the war so is, one</p>
        </body>
